com.stripe.stripepos.adapter.bbpos

Class BbposBluetoothAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stripe.stripepos.adapter.Adapter
      • com.stripe.stripepos.adapter.bbpos.BbposBluetoothAdapter

  • public class BbposBluetoothAdapter
extends Adapter
    The BbposBluetoothAdapter implements the Adapter interface to handle connecting and interacting with the BBPOS Chipper 2X device via Bluetooth.
